the concept of performance is
the last thing on their minds.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:09,580
Most app development is a mad
sprint towards getting features in,

4
00:00:09,580 --> 00:00:14,350
making the UI look perfect, and figuring
out a viable monetization strategy, or

5
00:00:14,350 --> 00:00:16,790
a lack thereof if you're
in Silicon Valley.

6
00:00:16,790 --> 00:00:19,870
But application performance is a lot
like the plumbing in your house.

7
00:00:19,870 --> 00:00:22,690
When it's working great, no one
really notices or thinks about it.

8
00:00:22,690 --> 00:00:25,780
But when something goes wrong,
suddenly, it's everyone's problem.

9
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:31,330
You see, users notice bad performance
before any other features in your app.

10
00:00:31,330 --> 00:00:34,620
Before your social widgets,
awesome image filters, and

11
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:37,150
