languages is Klingon.

12
00:00:37,150 --> 00:00:40,070
And guess what users unhappy with
performance give bad reviews

13
00:00:40,070 --> 00:00:42,550
at a higher percentage than any
other problems in your app.

14
00:00:42,550 --> 00:00:45,130
This is why we like to
say that perf matters.

15
00:00:45,130 --> 00:00:47,770
It's easy little side of performance
as you're developing your app.

16
00:00:47,770 --> 00:00:50,480
But frankly perf is involved
in everything you do.

17
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:51,720
Users feel bad performance.

18
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:53,280
They complain about bad performance.

19
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:54,220
They uninstall your app, and

20
00:00:54,220 --> 00:00:57,260
then vengefully give you a bad
review all because of performance.

21
00:00:57,260 --> 00:00:58,100
When you think of it this way,

22
00:00:58,100 --> 00:01:01,030
performance sounds more like
a feature that you should focus on,

23
00:01:01,030 --> 00:01:03,240
